# Jack Evertzberg Development – Mind‑Map & High‑Level Gantt (v0.2)

> **Purpose of this canvas:** provide a visual‑text framework we can iterate on together. Feel free to comment, reorder, or add branches/dates. 🔄

---

## 🗺️ Mind‑Map (Hierarchical Outline)

```
Jack Evertzberg Development
├── Vision & Positioning
│   ├─ Purpose: flagship mixed‑use waterfront
│   └─ Brand Promise: “Caribbean elegance reimagined”
├── Master‑Plan Zoning (1.2 M m²)
│   ├─ Luxury Tourist Zone (450 k m²)
│   │   ├─ Iconic Hotels & Resorts
│   │   ├─ Cultural Village (museums, art, markets)
│   │   ├─ Entertainment Hub (bars, convention ctr.)
│   │   ├─ Retail Promenade (luxury boutiques)
│   │   └─ Sustainable Ops (zero‑waste, renewables)
│   ├─ Exclusive Residential Communities (400 k m²)
│   │   ├─ Oceanfront Villas & Estates
│   │   ├─ Gated Neighborhoods (smart homes)
│   │   ├─ Private Island Development
│   │   ├─ Community Amenities (clubs, schools)
│   │   └─ Green Living Initiatives (EV, gardens)
│   └─ Recreational & Green Spaces (350 k m²)
│       ├─ Championship Golf Course
│       ├─ Equestrian Center & Track
│       ├─ Marina & Super‑Yacht Club
│       ├─ Adventure Park (zip lines, trails)
│       └─ Conservation Zones (reef program)
├── Technology & Innovation
│   ├─ Smart‑City Layer (IoT, 5G mesh)
│   ├─ Blockchain Integration (tokenization)
│   ├─ XR / VR (digital twins, AR way‑finding)
│   └─ Net‑Zero Path (solar, desalination, recycling)
├── Phased Development
│   ├─ Phase 1 – Foundation & Early Activation (Y1)
│   │   ├─ Infrastructure & Utilities
│   │   ├─ Beach Club Soft Launch
│   │   └─ Sales Gallery / Marketing Center
│   ├─ Phase 2 – Residential & Tourist Uplift (Y2‑3)
│   │   ├─ Villa Cluster #1
│   │   ├─ Hotel Tower #1
│   │   └─ Marina Basin
│   └─ Phase 3 – Completion & Enhancement (Y4‑5)
│       ├─ Golf Course & Equestrian Complex
│       ├─ Resort Grand Opening
│       └─ Full AI Property Platform Go‑Live
├── Financial & Partnerships
│   ├─ Capital Stack (seed, Series‑A, green bonds, token sale)
│   ├─ Revenue Streams (real‑estate, ADR/F&B, marina, memberships)
│   └─ Target IRR 18‑22 %
├── Governance & ESG
│   ├─ Regulatory Alignment & Permits
│   ├─ Construction Risk Mgmt (BIM, EPC contracts)
│   ├─ Social License (jobs, skills‑transfer)
│   └─ Climate Resilience (4 m FFE, stormwater grid)
└── 90‑Day Sprint
    ├─ Master‑Plan Refinement
    ├─ Permitting Package (EIA scope)
    ├─ Capital Stack Teaser & Data‑Room
    ├─ Brand & Go‑To‑Market (microsite, VR demo)
    └─ Community Engagement (town‑halls)
```

