## ⚠️ Risk & Contingency Register (living sidebar)

| # | Risk                           | Prob. | Impact | Mitigation                                                          | **Owner**    |
| - | ------------------------------ | ----- | ------ | ------------------------------------------------------------------- | ------------ |
| 1 | Construction cost inflation    | Med   | High   | Fixed‑price EPC contracts, early bulk‑buy of steel & concrete       | CFO          |
| 2 | Zoning / permit delays         | Med   | High   | Dedicated legal counsel, proactive govt liaison, buffer in schedule | Legal & ESG  |
| 3 | FX rate volatility (USD ↔ ANG) | High  | Med    | Hedge via forward contracts, multi‑currency escrow                  | CFO          |
| 4 | Hurricane event                | Low   | High   | 4 m FFE, Cat‑5 façades, business‑interruption insurance             | Dev Director |
| 5 | Community opposition           | Low   | Med    | Monthly town‑halls, local hiring targets, CSR fund                  | CSR Lead     |
| 6 | Tech integration overruns      | Med   | Med    | Agile sprints, phased roll‑out, vendor SLAs                         | CTO          |

> *Register reviewed monthly; update probability/impact as project evolves.*

