## 📅 90‑Day Sprint Board (Weeks 1‑18)

| Sprint | Calendar Weeks\* | Epic Focus             | Key Deliverables (JIRA‑style)                                                               | Owner(s)                           | DoD / Acceptance                             |
| ------ | ---------------- | ---------------------- | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- | ---------------------------------- | -------------------------------------------- |
| 1      | W1‑2             | Master‑Plan Refinement | • Kick‑off workshop<br>• Baseline data pack compiled<br>• Scope freeze for master‑plan v0.3 | Dev Director (R), Lead Planner (A) | Scope sign‑off logged in Confluence          |
| 2      | W3‑4             | Permitting Package     | • Draft EIA outline<br>• Stakeholder matrix<br>• Govt pre‑consult booked                    | Legal & ESG (R), CSR Lead (C)      | EIA outline uploaded; meeting date confirmed |
| 3      | W5‑6             | Capital Stack Teaser   | • Investor teaser deck v1<br>• Data‑room architecture ready                                 | CFO (R), CMO (C)                   | Teaser sent to 3 target funds                |
| 4      | W7‑8             | Brand & Go‑To‑Market   | • Naming workshop output<br>• Brand mood‑board<br>• Website wireframe                       | CMO (R), Hospitality Lead (C)      | Brand board approved; Figma wireframe signed |
| 5      | W9‑10            | Master‑Plan Refinement | • BIM clash‑check v1<br>• Cost plan update ±10 %                                            | Dev Director (R), QS (C)           | BIM exported; cost variance < 10 %           |
| 6      | W11‑12           | Community Engagement   | • Town‑hall #1 executed<br>• Press release draft<br>• Local vendor registry kick‑off        | CSR Lead (R), CMO (C)              | >50 attendees; media pickup secured          |
| 7      | W13‑14           | Permitting Package     | • EIA draft §§ 1‑3<br>• Zoning amendment draft                                              | Legal & ESG (R), Lead Planner (C)  | Internal legal review complete               |
| 8      | W15‑16           | Capital Stack Teaser   | • Financial model v0.9<br>• Debt term‑sheet shortlist                                       | CFO (R), Residential PM (C)        | Model audited; 3 lenders engaged             |
| 9      | W17‑18           | Brand & XR Launch      | • VR demo v1<br>• Microsite live<br>• Influencer fam‑trip plan                              | CMO (R), CTO (C)                   | VR demo playable; microsite uptime ≥99 %     |

> *Assumes project start at Month 0. Dates to be finalized at kickoff.*

