## 🗓️ Five‑Year Strategic Plan (Y0 → Y5)

| Year    | Strategic Theme                                      | Top‑Line Objectives                                                              | Major Deliverables                                                                                                             | KPIs / Success Metrics                                                                             |
| ------- | ---------------------------------------------------- | -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------ | -------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| **0‑1** | **Foundation & Early Activation**                    | • Secure permits & utilities<br>• Launch brand awareness<br>• Kick‑off presales  | • Utilities commissioned (💎 M01‑06)<br>• Beach Club & Sales Gallery ready (M04‑12)<br>• Master‑Plan v0.3 locked               | • 100 % utilities online<br>• ≥30 % villa presales<br>• Social‑license sentiment > 70 % positive   |
| **1‑2** | **Residential & Tourist Uplift**                     | • Build initial residential & hotel inventory<br>• Activate marina basin         | • Villa Cluster #1 topped‑out (💎 M24)<br>• Hotel Tower #1 topped‑out (💎 M28)<br>• Marina dredging complete (💎 M26)          | • ≥60 % villas sold<br>• Hotel ADR forecast hit 90 % of pro‑forma<br>• Yacht berth bookings > 50 % |
| **2‑3** | **Revenue Ramp & Amenities Build‑Out**               | • Open hotel soft and drive occupancy<br>• Finalize golf & equestrian earthworks | • Soft‑open hotel floors 1‑10 (M32‑36)<br>• Begin golf course grassing (M36)<br>• Equestrian complex structural complete (M40) | • Hotel occupancy ≥ 65 % <br>• F\&B capture ≥ 45 %<br>• 3 signature events hosted                  |
| **3‑4** | **Experiential Enhancement & Community Integration** | • Complete golf, equestrian, adventure park<br>• Scale smart‑city & AI platform  | • Golf course grassing complete (💎 M44)<br>• AI property‑mgmt beta (M46)<br>• Adventure park ribbon‑cutting (M48)             | • Customer NPS ≥ 70<br>• Energy from renewables ≥ 35 %<br>• 500 local jobs created                 |
| **4‑5** | **Grand Opening & Optimization**                     | • Full resort opening & brand launch<br>• Optimize ops & financial performance   | • Resort soft‑opening (💎 M54)<br>• Grand Opening Gala (M60)<br>• Tokenization Phase‑2 rollout                                 | • IRR run‑rate ≥ 18 %<br>• Resort RevPAR ≥ 110 % of comp set<br>• ESG KPIs met for LEED Gold       |

> *KPIs reviewed quarterly; adjust targets as data matures.*

